         MNOTE *,'Generating SWAREQPL mapping macro'                    00750000
SWAREQPL DSECT                                                          00760000
SWARQPL  DS    0XL8                    * Define whole SWAREQPL          00770000
SWAEPAL  DS    AL4                     * Pointer to EPAL/EPAX           00780000
SWAFCD   DS    AL4                     * Pointer to function code       00790000
.*                                     * CL2'RL' or CL2'WL'             00800000
SWAREQPL_LEN EQU *-SWAREQPL            * Length of parmlist             00810000
